Straight Path Communications Inc (STRP) CEO & PRESIDENT Davidi Jonas Sold $5.4 million of Shares


July 07, 2017, 06:15:01 PM EDT
By insider, GuruFocus









































Shutterstock photo


CEO & PRESIDENT of Straight Path Communications Inc ( STRP ) Davidi Jonas sold 30,000 shares of STRP on 07/05/2017 at an average price of $179.6 a share. The total sale was $5.4 million.Straight Path Communications Inc provides services to internet service and telecommunications providers. It holds licenses for fixed wireless spectrum in the United States, providing broad geographic coverage. Straight Path Communications Inc has a market cap of $2.29 billion; its shares were traded at around $180.00 with and P/S ratio of 3529.36.CEO Recent Trades:CEO & PRESIDENT Davidi Jonas sold 30,000 shares of STRP stock on 07/05/2017 at the average price of $179.6. The price of the stock has increased by 0.22% since.CEO & PRESIDENT Davidi Jonas sold 9,395 shares of STRP stock on 06/14/2017 at the average price of $179.94. The price of the stock has increased by 0.03% since.CFO Recent Trades:CFO Jonathan Rand sold 4,134 shares of STRP stock on 06/27/2017 at the average price of $179.86. The price of the stock has increased by 0.08% since.Directors and Officers Recent Trades:GENERAL COUNSEL David L Breau sold 575 shares of STRP stock on 06/22/2017 at the average price of $179.53. The price of the stock has increased by 0.26% since.GENERAL COUNSEL David L Breau sold 1,935 shares of STRP stock on 06/21/2017 at the average price of $179.85. The price of the stock has increased by 0.08% since.Director Fred S Zeidman sold 5,000 shares of STRP stock on 06/19/2017 at the average price of $179.59. The price of the stock has increased by 0.23% since.10% Owner Howard S Jonas sold 84,523 shares of STRP stock on 06/16/2017 at the average price of $179.51. The price of the stock has increased by 0.27% since.10% Owner Howard S Jonas sold 18,217 shares of STRP stock on 06/15/2017 at the average price of $179.76. The price of the stock has increased by 0.13% since.click here

